text: Suturoglypta blignautae is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Columbellidae, the dove snails. ==Description== Its shell size is 11.2 mm ==Distribution== This species can be found along South Africa. ==References== Category:Columbellidae Category:Gastropods described in 1998 Category:Invertebrates of South Africa
title: Suturoglypta blignautae
